title: kidsme food feeder plus
description: kidsme Food Feeder Plus is the newest addition to our Food Feeder Family. It features a larger, flexible silicone sac to satisfy a baby’s growing appetite. The ergonomics consideration on sac let babies become much enjoyable when using the Food Feeder Plus. It is also included a egg-shaped case, which is not only as food container for food feeder, but also a grinding tool when preparing food for babies and a food container that makes food preparation and storage quick and easy. With the same great benefits of the kidsme Food Feeder, it is a feeding essential that allows babies to taste nearly twice as much fresh food safely.
